Chadi Riad doubled the lead by the 16th minute

Post-Match Reflections: Walid Regragui, the Moroccan coach, praised the team's performance and highlighted the changes in formation

Miscellaneous Highlights: This win strengthens Morocco's lead in the 2026 World Cup qualifiers
